nodes.text: Star Wars 95 is the ninety-fifth issue of the Legends comic book series Star Wars. It was written by Mary Jo Duffy, illustrated by Cynthia Martin, and first published on February 12, 1985 by Marvel Comics. The issue features the story "No Zeltrons," which culminates in a climactic duel between Luke Skywalker and the Dark Lady Lumiya.
There's a new Dark Lord in the galaxy, and she's out for Luke's head! Not only must Luke fight Lumiya, he must also deal with who and, more dangerously, what she really is!
